5:["$","$L10",null,{"project":{"_id":"b1e4d5c4-7d33-4bad-8e1d-3053cbdcf0f6","body":{"conclusion":"The HAZOP exercise produced a comprehensive safety dossier now in use by the facility's HSE department. Implementing the recommended controls is projected to reduce incident probability in the identified zones by over 60%.","methodology":"Each node of the steam system was examined using structured guidewords (No, More, Less, Reverse, Other). Temperature mapping was performed using thermal imaging. Findings were cross-referenced with OSHA 29 CFR 1910 and local HSE regulations to assign risk ratings.","overview":"Conducted within a food-grade manufacturing facility, this study performed a systematic HAZOP (Hazard and Operability Study) on steam distribution lines and high-temperature surface zones. The objective was to document existing hazards, assess risk levels, and propose mitigation measures aligned with HSE standards.","results":"Identified 14 high-priority hazard nodes, 9 of which required immediate engineering controls. Proposed insulation retrofits for 6 steam lines and developed a lockout/tagout (LOTO) protocol for maintenance activities in restricted zones."},"category":"Utilities Engineering","description":"Detailed steam and hot surface hazard analysis within food manufacturing environments, establishing robust plant operation documentation.","featured":true,"id":"b1e4d5c4-7d33-4bad-8e1d-3053cbdcf0f6","images":[{"alt":"Plant layout overview","asset":{"_ref":"image-b63631be9bf8b2683eae7c27642fd3b5263edc98-4032x3024-jpg","_type":"reference"},"src":"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/c2t45jcn/production/b63631be9bf8b2683eae7c27642fd3b5263edc98-4032x3024.jpg"},{"alt":"Steam line schematic","asset":{"_ref":"image-c8b9598dd8ca34a555d132028c4f115367de387b-6024x4024-jpg","_type":"reference"},"src":"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/c2t45jcn/production/c8b9598dd8ca34a555d132028c4f115367de387b-6024x4024.jpg"},{"alt":"Hazard zone mapping","asset":{"_ref":"image-cd35a6582433cf9b4e35bde810ca5ffa344819e6-5472x3648-jpg","_type":"reference"},"src":"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/c2t45jcn/production/cd35a6582433cf9b4e35bde810ca5ffa344819e6-5472x3648.jpg"}],"slug":"plant-hazard-safety-studies","title":"Plant Hazard & Safety Studies","year":"2023"}}]
